"13:12:6" : {s: 13, a: 12, w: 6, r: "طمع", t: "وَطَمَعًۭا", l: "طَمَع", lc: 4, tl: "waṭamaʿan", lb: "লোভ করা, কামনা করা, প্রত্যাশা করা,",e: "and a hope", b: "ও প্রত্যাশা (নিয়ে)", i: "dan harapan", f: 4, rm: "to covet, eagerly desire, long or hope for, yearn for. tamaun - desire, hoping and longing for, causing to be full of hope."},
"13:12:7" : {s: 13, a: 12, w: 7, r: "نشا", t: "وَيُنشِئُ", l: "أَنشَأَ", lc: 20, tl: "wayunshi-u", lb: "সৃষ্টি করা, তৈরী করা",e: "and brings up", b: "সৃষ্টি করেন", i: "dan Dia mengadakan", f: 1, rm: "lived, arose, become elevated/high, grow up, create/produce/originate, it happened/occurred, raise, to found/build, began, specifically discussing 73:6,rising in the night, first part/hours of the night, every hour of the night in which one rises, every hour of the night."},
